r justify-between gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[11px] text-kvrn-muted tracking-wide\",\"children\":[\"© \",2026,\" KVRN. All rights reserved.\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[11px] text-kvrn-subtle\",\"children\":\"Prices shown in selected currency. Conversion is approximate.\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"hidden sm:block text-[11px] text-kvrn-border\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\",\"children\":\"·\"}],[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"mailto:support@kvrn.shop\",\"className\":\"text-[11px] text-kvrn-subtle hover:text-kvrn-muted transition-colors duration-150 tracking-wide\",\"children\":\"support@kvrn.shop\"}]]}]]}]\n11:[\"$\",\"$L17\",null,{}]\n12:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L9\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"error\":\"$undefined\",\"errorStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"errorScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$La\",null,{}],\"templateStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"templateScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"notFound\":\"$undefined\",\"forbidden\":\"$undefined\",\"unauthorized\":\"$undefined\"}]]}]\n13:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L9\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"error\":\"$undefined\",\"errorStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"errorScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$La\",null,{}],\"templateStyles\":\"$undefined\",\"templateScripts\":\"$undefined\",\"notFound\":\"$undefined\",\"forbidden\":\"$undefined\",\"unauthorized\":\"$undefined\"}]]}]\n14:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"pt-[calc(36px+56px)]\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-kvrn section-padding max-w-3xl\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"nav\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"Breadcrumb\",\"className\":\"mb-10\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-kvrn-muted tracking-wide\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$Lb\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"className\":\"hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Home\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":\"true\",\"children\":\"·\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"text-kvrn-text\",\"aria-current\":\"page\",\"children\":\"FAQ\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"font-display font-light text-[40px] md:text-[56px] leading-none tracking-tighter mb-16\",\"children\":\"Questions\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-16\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"section\",\"Product\",{\"id\":\"$undefined\",\"aria-labelledby\":\"section-Product\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"section-Product\",\"className\":\"label-11 mb-6\",\"children\":\"Product\"}],[\"$\",\"$L18\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"what-is-400-gsm\",\"trigger\":\"What does 400 GSM mean?\",\"content\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"GSM stands for grams per square metre — the standard measurement of fabric weight. A higher number means a denser, heavier fabric.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Most hoodies on the market are 280–320 GSM. At 300 GSM, a hoodie feels light and somewhat provisional. At 400 GSM+, the fabric becomes structural — it holds its shape, drapes differently, and has a perceptible weight when you hold it.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"KVRN is developed around heavyweight fleece construction. Full material specifications are listed on every product page.\"}]]}]},{\"id\":\"why-no-drawstring\",\"trigger\":\"Why is there no drawstring?\",\"content\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The 3-panel hood is engineered to hold its form without a drawstring. A drawstring is typically added because the hood collapses without it — the hood requires external support to maintain shape. KVRN's hood structure eliminates that requirement. There is nothing to pull, nothing to lose, and nothing to interrupt the silhouette.\"}]},{\"id\":\"hidden-zippers\",\"trigger\":\"How do the hidden zippers work?\",\"content\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Each kangaroo pocket opening has a concealed YKK coil zipper running parallel behind it — one on each side. From the outside, with the zipper closed, the pockets appear completely standard. Open the zipper and you have access to a secure interior compartment. They are invisible in all positions.\"}]},{\"id\":\"care\",\"trigger\":\"How should I wash and care for the hoodie?\",\"content\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Machine wash cold (30°C), inside out. Use a gentle cycle. Air dry — do not tumble dry. Do not iron the rubber patch.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The fleece will soften over the first 3–5 washes. This is expected behaviour — the fabric continues to improve with regular wear and care. The structure of the hood and the integrity of the zippers are not affected by washing.\"}]]}]},{\"id\":\"fabric\",\"trigger\":\"What is the fabric composition?\",\"content\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"100% ring-spun combed cotton. No polyester blend. Ring-spun cotton is stronger and softer than standard spun cotton due to the way the fibres are twisted. Combing removes short fibres and impurities, resulting in a cleaner, more durable yarn.\"}]}]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",\"Sizing\",{\"id\":\"sizing\",\"aria-labelledby\":\"section-Sizing\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"section-Sizing\",\"className\":\"label-11 mb-6\",\"children\":\"Sizing\"}],[\"$\",\"$L18\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"sizing-guide\",\"trigger\":\"How does KVRN fit?\",\"content\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"KVRN is designed to be oversized. This is not a standard fit with extra room — it is a considered oversized silhouette where the proportions are deliberate.\"}],\"$L19\",\"$L1a\"]}]},{\"id\":\"between-sizes\",\"trigger\":\"I am between sizes — what should I do?\",\"content\":\"$L1b\"}]}]]}],\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\"]}],\"$L1e\"]}]}],null,\"$L1f\"]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[[\"$\",\"$L20\",null,{\"children\":\"$L21\"}],null],[\"$\",\"$L22\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$23\",null,{\"fallback\":null,\"children\":\"$L24\"}]}]}]]}]\n25:I[4431,[],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n27:I[5278,[],\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\"]\n19:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"If you want the intended silhouette, buy your normal size. If you prefer a cleaner, more fitted oversized look, size down.\"}]\n1a:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"overflow-x-auto mt-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"table\",null,{\"className\":\"w-full text-[13px]\",\"aria-label\":\"Size guide measurements\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"thead\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-kvrn-border\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\",\"children\":\"Size\"}],[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\",\"children\":\"Chest (cm)\"}],[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\",\"children\":\"Length (cm)\"}],[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"text-left py-2 font-light label-11\",\"children\":\"Sleeve (cm)\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"tbody\",null,{\"className\":\"divide-y divide-kvrn-border\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"tr\",\"XS\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2.5 font-light\",\"children\":\"XS\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2.5 text-kvrn-muted\",\"children\":60}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2.5 text-kvrn-muted\",\"children\":72}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2.5 text-kvrn-muted\",\"children\":63}]]}],[\"$\",\"tr\",\"S\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2.5 font-light\",\"children\":\"S\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2.5 text-kvrn-muted\",\"children\":64}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2.5 te